    "updated_at": "2015-01-16T22:20:00Z",
    "body": "> If there is a simple way to \"catch\" a fail! I would like to hear about it and fix this.\n\nThere is no way to catch a `panic!`, by design. It ends the current `Thread`. So, the only way to fix this kind of thing would be to run each plugin in its own thread...\n",
